<sect1 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md182">
<title>构建和发布流程</title><sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md183">
<title>1. 准备发布</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md184">
<title>1.1 更新版本号</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>使用版本管理脚本</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">./bump_version.sh<sp/>0.2.0</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>这将自动更新：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>pyproject.toml</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="client__sdk_2src_2p2p__sdk_2____init_____8py" kindref="compound">src/p2p_sdk/__init__.py</ref></computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>conda/meta.yaml</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_8md" kindref="compound">CHANGELOG.md</ref></computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md186">
<title>1.2 更新 CHANGELOG</title><para>编辑 <computeroutput><ref refid="_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_8md" kindref="compound">CHANGELOG.md</ref></computeroutput>，添加本次发布的详细变更：</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".markdown"><codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>[0.2.0]<sp/>-<sp/>2026-03-20</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Added</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>新功能<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>新功能<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Changed</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>改进<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>改进<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Fixed</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>修复<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>修复<sp/>2</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md188">
<title>1.3 运行测试</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行所有测试</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pytest<sp/>tests/<sp/>-v</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>检查覆盖率</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pytest<sp/>--cov=p2p_sdk<sp/>tests/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行类型检查</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">mypy<sp/>src/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行代码格式检查</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">black<sp/>--check<sp/>src/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ruff<sp/>check<sp/>src/</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md189">
<title>2. 构建包</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md191">
<title>2.1 构建 Python Wheel</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行构建脚本</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">./build.sh</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>这将：<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>清理旧的构建文件</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>安装构建依赖</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>构建 wheel 和 sdist</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>验证包完整性</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>输出文件位于 <computeroutput>dist/</computeroutput> 目录：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>p2p_sdk-0.2.0-py3-none-any.whl</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>p2p_sdk-0.2.0.tar.gz</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md194">
<title>2.2 构建 Conda 包</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行<sp/>conda<sp/>构建脚本</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>conda</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">./build.sh</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md197">
<title>3. 本地测试</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md198">
<title>3.1 测试 Wheel 包</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>创建虚拟环境</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python3<sp/>-m<sp/>venv<sp/>test_env</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">source<sp/>test_env/bin/activate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>安装构建的包</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>dist/p2p_sdk-0.2.0-py3-none-any.whl</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>测试导入</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;from<sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/>import<sp/>P2PClient;<sp/>print(&apos;OK&apos;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>运行示例</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>examples/basic_usage.py</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>清理</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">deactivate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">rm<sp/>-rf<sp/>test_env</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md199">
<title>3.2 测试 Conda 包</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>安装本地包</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">conda<sp/>install<sp/>--use-local<sp/>p2p-sdk</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>测试</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;from<sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/>import<sp/>P2PClient;<sp/>print(&apos;OK&apos;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>卸载</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">conda<sp/>remove<sp/>p2p-sdk</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md200">
<title>4. 发布到 Test PyPI</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md201">
<title>4.1 配置凭证</title><para>复制模板并填写 Test PyPI token：</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">cp<sp/>.pypirc.template<sp/>~/.pypirc</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>编辑<sp/>~/.pypirc，填写<sp/>testpypi<sp/>token</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md202">
<title>4.2 上传到 Test PyPI</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>上传到<sp/>Test<sp/>PyPI</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">./publish.sh<sp/>test</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md203">
<title>4.3 从 Test PyPI 安装测试</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>创建测试环境</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python3<sp/>-m<sp/>venv<sp/>test_pypi_env</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">source<sp/>test_pypi_env/bin/activate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>从<sp/>Test<sp/>PyPI<sp/>安装</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>--index-url<sp/>https://test.pypi.org/simple/<sp/>p2p-sdk</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>测试</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;from<sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/>import<sp/>P2PClient;<sp/>print(&apos;OK&apos;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>清理</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">deactivate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">rm<sp/>-rf<sp/>test_pypi_env</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md204">
<title>5. 发布到生产 PyPI</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md205">
<title>5.1 最终检查</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem override="unchecked"><para>所有测试通过</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem override="unchecked"><para>文档已更新</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem override="unchecked"><para>CHANGELOG 已更新</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem override="unchecked"><para>版本号正确</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem override="unchecked"><para>Test PyPI 测试成功</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md207">
<title>5.2 创建 Git 标签</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>提交版本变更</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>add<sp/>-A</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>commit<sp/>-m<sp/>&quot;chore:<sp/>bump<sp/>version<sp/>to<sp/>0.2.0&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>创建标签</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>tag<sp/>-a<sp/>v0.2.0<sp/>-m<sp/>&quot;Release<sp/>v0.2.0&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>推送到远程</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>push<sp/>origin<sp/>main</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>push<sp/>origin<sp/>v0.2.0</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md208">
<title>5.3 上传到 PyPI</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>上传到生产<sp/>PyPI</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">./publish.sh<sp/>prod</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md210">
<title>5.4 验证发布</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>等待几分钟让<sp/>PyPI<sp/>索引更新</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">sleep<sp/>60</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>安装并测试</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>p2p-sdk==0.2.0</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;from<sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/>import<sp/>P2PClient;<sp/>print(&apos;OK&apos;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md212">
<title>6. 发布到 Conda</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md213">
<title>6.1 上传到 Anaconda Cloud</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>获取包路径</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PACKAGE_PATH=$(conda-build<sp/>conda/<sp/>--output)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>上传</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">anaconda<sp/>upload<sp/>$PACKAGE_PATH</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md215">
<title>6.2 验证</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>从<sp/>Anaconda<sp/>Cloud<sp/>安装</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">conda<sp/>install<sp/>-c<sp/>your-channel<sp/>p2p-sdk</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>测试</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;from<sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/>import<sp/>P2PClient;<sp/>print(&apos;OK&apos;)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md216">
<title>7. 发布 GitHub Release</title><sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md218">
<title>7.1 创建 Release</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>访问 GitHub 仓库</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>点击 &quot;Releases&quot; → &quot;Create a new release&quot;</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>选择标签 <computeroutput>v0.2.0</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>填写 Release 标题：<computeroutput>v0.2.0</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>复制 CHANGELOG 内容到描述</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>上传构建产物：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>dist/p2p_sdk-0.2.0-py3-none-any.whl</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>dist/p2p_sdk-0.2.0.tar.gz</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>点击 &quot;Publish release&quot;</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect3>
<sect3 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_r_e_l_e_a_s_e___g_u_i_d_e_1autotoc_md221">
<title>7.2 更新文档</title><para>如果使用 GitHub Pages 或 Read the Docs：</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>构建文档</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>docs</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>html</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>部署到<sp/>GitHub<sp/>Pages</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>（根据你的文档托管方式）</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
</sect1>
